OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRestaurants set to be      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbanned from withholding    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstaff tips                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Restaurant, cafe and pub bosses are set
OL,6, to be banned from keeping tips left for
OL,7, staff by customers in Britain.         
OL,9,FThe government plans to make it illegal
OL,10,Ffor hospitality firms to withhold tips 
OL,11,Ffrom workers, who often rely on them to
OL,12,Ftop up their income.                   
OL,14,FLabour Markets Minister Paul Scully    
OL,15,Fsaid the plans would "ensure tips will 
OL,16,Fgo to those who worked for it".        
OL,18,FIf an employer breaks the new rules    
OL,19,Fthey can be taken to an employment     
OL,20,Ftribunal.                              
